snippet.title: iHasCupquake
snippet.description:
Heyo! My name is Tiffy but many know me as Cupquake. I am a variety gamer attracted to the cute and dark side of things. I upload almost daily content ranging from horror, indie, puzzle...anything that sparks my interest really. I am also an artist and love sharing creations driven by art, music and expression.
♥ 
I livestream 3 times a week over on Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/ihascupquake

We also create some pretty unique stuff! Check out our store -  http://bit.ly/2WjnCBI

Channel Rules:
-Be respectful to us and everyone in the comment section
- Negative/hateful comments will not be tolerated and will result in an immediate ban from the channel
-We're all about constructive criticism, as it helps us improve our videos
-Please be yourself, respect others, and have fun with the channel! :D
♥
Contact:
Fan mail - Fanmail@ihascupquake.com
